WEBVTT

00:00:15.681 --> 00:00:17.076
The Fire Seed shattered!

00:00:17.342 --> 00:00:18.575
And Nahida's, she's...!

00:00:19.275 --> 00:00:19.977
I know

00:00:20.456 --> 00:00:22.248
A sacrifice must be made

00:00:22.892 --> 00:00:24.578
But not by the Lord of Dendro

00:00:28.128 --> 00:00:30.325
We've all grown on this long journey

00:00:32.705 --> 00:00:35.595
If the purpose of that growth was to return home

00:00:36.260 --> 00:00:37.975
Then our wishes have come true

00:00:45.994 --> 00:00:47.750
Would you lend us your power?

00:00:51.478 --> 00:00:53.140
You knew it would come to this...

00:00:53.681 --> 00:00:54.917
All the knowledge

00:00:55.548 --> 00:00:56.215
Language

00:00:56.675 --> 00:00:58.204
And emotions that you have learned

00:00:58.943 --> 00:01:02.137
Will be reverted into pure elemental energy

00:01:04.506 --> 00:01:05.905
In your new homeland

00:01:06.245 --> 00:01:08.203
Nothing of who you were will remain

00:01:09.720 --> 00:01:11.606
You won't be remembered by anyone...

00:01:12.209 --> 00:01:13.240
Is that truly...

00:01:13.829 --> 00:01:15.802
The return you've always dreamed of?

00:01:17.098 --> 00:01:18.698
Lord of Dendro

00:01:18.831 --> 00:01:20.762
Don't be sad

00:01:21.237 --> 00:01:22.511
This is not

00:01:22.511 --> 00:01:23.983
Your home

00:01:25.132 --> 00:01:25.779
We

00:01:25.779 --> 00:01:26.998
Go home

00:01:27.742 --> 00:01:29.131
Lord of Dendro

00:01:29.350 --> 00:01:30.655
Should also

00:01:30.796 --> 00:01:31.930
Go home

00:01:42.817 --> 00:01:43.817
Hear us please

00:01:44.553 --> 00:01:46.378
Feel our heartfelt desires!

00:01:47.707 --> 00:01:48.375
Awaken!

